name: Rupert Resources Ltd.
longDescription: Rupert Resources Ltd is engaged in the acquisition and exploration of mineral properties in Finland. The company owns the Pahtavaara gold mine, mill and exploration permits and concessions, including the Ikkari prospect, all located in the central Lapland greenstone belt in Northern Finland. Its other project include Hirsikangas. It operates in one reportable operating segment, being the acquisition and exploration of mineral properties in Finland.
